  <slide>
    <title>Accessibility Policies in Illinois</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Illinois Board of Higher Education (IBHE) Disability Access Initiative</li>
        <li>Required all campuses to survey for students with disabilities</li>
        <li>Wanted to set a State Standard on Web Accessibility</li>
        <li>Got a web accessibility reporting requirement as part of annual underrepresented minority student report</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
